text: Henry Hiatt (born 1868, date of death unknown) was a British gymnast. He competed in the men's individual all-around event at the 1900 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1868 births Category:Year of death missing Category:British male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Great Britain Category:Gymnasts at the 1900 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from London
